        "endTime": 5.164,
        "duration": 3.114,
        "sentenceIndex": 25
      },
      {
        "text": "Lisa had no money saved.",
        "startTime": 5.164,
        "endTime": 6.987,
        "duration": 1.823,
        "sentenceIndex": 26
      },
      {
        "text": "She lost her job just before the accident happened.",
        "startTime": 6.987,
        "endTime": 10.86,
        "duration": 3.873,
        "sentenceIndex": 27
      },
      {
        "text": "It was hard to support three children now.",
        "startTime": 10.86,
        "endTime": 14.05,
        "duration": 3.19,
        "sentenceIndex": 28
      },
      {
        "text": "She has no family nearby to help her.",
        "startTime": 14.05,
        "endTime": 16.86,
        "duration": 2.81,
        "sentenceIndex": 29
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 16.860023,
    "measuredDuration": 16.860023
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b5",
    "bundleIndex": 5,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/single-parent-rising-1/A1/bundle-5.mp3",
    "audioPath": "single-parent-rising-1/A1/bundle-5.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
        "text": "Lisa moved into a small apartment with her children, James, Emily, and baby Noah.",
        "startTime": 0,
        "endTime": 6.226,
        "duration": 6.226,
        "sentenceIndex": 30
      },
      {
        "text": "The apartment was tiny, but they made it home.",
        "startTime": 6.226,
        "endTime": 9.656,
        "duration": 3.43,
        "sentenceIndex": 31
      },
      {
        "text": "Lisa wanted work, but it was hard to find a job.",
        "startTime": 9.656,
        "endTime": 13.229,
        "duration": 3.573,
        "sentenceIndex": 32
      },
      {
        "text": "Every day, she looked in the newspaper and online.",
        "startTime": 13.229,
        "endTime": 16.944,
        "duration": 3.715,
        "sentenceIndex": 33
      },
      {
        "text": "She took any job she could find and worked hard for money.",
        "startTime": 16.944,
        "endTime": 21.08,
        "duration": 4.136,
        "sentenceIndex": 34
      },
      {
        "text": "The work is hard and makes her very tired.",
        "startTime": 21.08,
        "endTime": 24.075,
        "duration": 2.995,
        "sentenceIndex": 35
      }
    ],
    "totalDuration": 24.07483,
    "measuredDuration": 24.07483
  },
  {
    "bundleId": "b6",
    "bundleIndex": 6,
    "audioUrl": "https://xsolwqqdbsuydwmmwtsl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/audio-files/single-parent-rising-1/A1/bundle-6.mp3",
    "audioPath": "single-parent-rising-1/A1/bundle-6.mp3",
    "sentences": [
      {
