        "endTime": 12.906,
        "duration": 3.447,
        "sentenceIndex": 62
      },
      {
        "text": "She felt hopeless but still hoped for a miracle.",
        "startTime": 12.906,
        "endTime": 16.426,
        "duration": 3.52,
        "sentenceIndex": 63
      },
      {
        "text": "The next morning, James came into Lisa's room.",
        "startTime": 16.426,
